{"tid":2194841,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【大圍襲警案】官：「高級警務人員喝令市民離開，咁就要離開？唔好意思！我唔接受。」","createTime":"2020-09-08T18:32:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T08:30:15.000Z","uid":240362,"like":91,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"fd51750314c8c2289c3272047e465ff38ff8b0f0","tid":2194841,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T18:32:27.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】網民去年9月1日在機場發起「和你塞」活動，警方當晚派出防暴警在多區搜捕，有一對互不認識的男女在港鐵大圍站被指襲警。案件昨續審，男被告供稱看見女被告遭警員無理推至牆邊，遂質問，其間有警員推他的未婚妻胸部，他為保護未婚妻，才會舉手擋住該警員。控方問他為何不依警員指示後退，署理主任裁判官溫紹明聞言說：「高級警務人員喝令市民離開，咁就要離開？唔好意思！我唔接受。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200909/LKLVGBJDGFE4BGSDIO4IX6AV3U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200909%2FLKLVGBJDGFE4BGSDIO4IX6AV3U%2F&d=pZTDRaRh7CFw%2FURiZY0DNVLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=b4e9e9ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200909%2FLKLVGBJDGFE4BGSDIO4IX6AV3U%2F&h=441c6dfe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200909/LKLVGBJDGFE4BGSDIO4IX6AV3U/</a>"},{"pid":"210ee4172d2683a023f99108f11444c240584b1e","tid":2194841,"uid":352936,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T18:33:46.000Z","msg":"正確，正常人都唔會理狗吠聲"},{"pid":"923c8abcca471a55f283f7b99b5539adbfdf7e5c","tid":2194841,"uid":109629,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T18:34:16.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"small\">其間有警員推他的未婚妻胸部</span><br />\n<br />\n成班強姦犯抽少陣水驚死蝕底咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bb6534064dadc0a5772d1e9b391226f33ed9f70","tid":2194841,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T18:35:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a55b66b32f1a7f1173fdb206707987f3b3de649","tid":2194841,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T18:36:39.000Z","msg":"黑警<i